{"id":1234,"date":"2025-04-12T00:10:37","date_gmt":"2025-04-11T17:10:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1234"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:38:08","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:38:08","slug":"nang-tone-body","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/nang-tone-body\/","title":{"rendered":"N\u00e2ng tone body"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t b\u1eadt tone da s\u00e1ng kho\u1ebb sau 90 ph\u00fat cho da \u0111en b\u1ea9m sinh, da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u00e0o th\u1ea3i melanin, da tr\u1eafng b\u1eadt tone ngay sau khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.<\/li>\n<li>Tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1, nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam nang l\u00f4ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1eafm tr\u1eafng phi thuy\u1ec1n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nguy\u00ean l\u00fd s\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec7t m\u00e1y phi thuy\u1ec1n, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da g\u1ea5p 3 &#8211; 5 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng kem \u1ee7 tr\u1eafng body GSC+ ch\u1ee9a Niacinamide 1.5%, Alpha Arbutin 5%, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t r\u1ec5 d\u00e2u t\u1eb1m v\u00e0 Collagen thu\u1ef7 ph\u00e2n, \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nano gi\u00fap d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da nhanh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 60-90 ph\u00fat<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 10 l\u1ea7n, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i kho\u1ea3ng 5-7 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -13px; top: 319.014px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t b\u1eadt tone da s\u00e1ng kho\u1ebb sau 90 ph\u00fat cho da \u0111en b\u1ea9m sinh, da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3651,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[41],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1234","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-nang-tone-body","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1234","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1234"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3651"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1234"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1234"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=1234"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=1234"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}